WEBVTT

01:34.960 --> 01:37.720
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL OF THE SAME NAME
BY ZHU YI ON WWW.JJWXC.NET

01:37.800 --> 01:42.520
BEIYU HIGH SCHOOL, SENIOR YEAR

01:42.600 --> 01:44.800
Sorry. I think I forgot to top up my card.

01:45.440 --> 01:46.480
Let me find some change.

02:25.280 --> 02:26.240
Thanks.

02:28.200 --> 02:30.240
Why don't we exchange contact info?

02:30.320 --> 02:31.880
I'll transfer the money to you later.

02:33.280 --> 02:34.480
It's fine. No need.

02:48.400 --> 02:49.240
4,055 DAYS

03:02.960 --> 03:03.960
Miss Zeng.

03:05.800 --> 03:08.880
Apparently, the suspect's
niece-in-law reported him.

03:12.480 --> 03:15.160
- I'll give it a try.
- Let me try.

03:15.880 --> 03:17.280
All right. Go ahead.

03:23.600 --> 03:24.920
Hello, Zeng Yi.

03:25.520 --> 03:26.480
I'm Wen Yifan,

03:27.360 --> 03:28.680
Wen Ming's cousin.

03:28.760 --> 03:30.920
Okay, I'll bring you there.

03:45.400 --> 03:48.800
I've learned a bit about your situation.

03:53.040 --> 03:55.240
I've been through the same thing.

04:04.960 --> 04:07.200
Back then, I dragged him
and jumped off the balcony together.

04:09.640 --> 04:10.960
At that moment,

04:11.840 --> 04:13.120
I thought maybe dying wasn't so bad.

04:15.440 --> 04:16.600
But later, I realized

04:16.680 --> 04:18.880
dying with someone like him
wasn't worth it.

04:20.279 --> 04:22.480
I used to be too scared
to sleep every night.

04:23.720 --> 04:25.040
Every time I closed my eyes,
all I saw was his face.

04:26.680 --> 04:27.960
That feeling…

04:29.120 --> 04:30.400
I know it all too well.

04:38.400 --> 04:39.560
I was just a kid then.

04:41.360 --> 04:42.720
All I could do was cry.

04:43.240 --> 04:44.880
I usually cried the whole night.

04:46.360 --> 04:47.760
But as the pain got worse,

04:49.120 --> 04:50.720
I grew quieter, little by little.

04:52.920 --> 04:55.120
Until one day,
I couldn't even cry anymore.

05:01.520 --> 05:03.960
Why do we have to suffer like this?

05:04.880 --> 05:06.120
Why?

05:09.840 --> 05:12.360
Can you tell me what happened that night?

05:40.800 --> 05:43.960
Uncle Che. You're home early today.

05:44.480 --> 05:45.320
Yeah.

05:49.040 --> 05:50.120
Where's Wen Ming?

05:50.640 --> 05:53.320
He's at a class reunion.
He'll be back soon.

05:53.400 --> 05:54.440
I'll head to my room now.

05:59.240 --> 06:00.240
You changed the body wash?

06:01.720 --> 06:03.200
That smells nice.

06:06.640 --> 06:08.520
Uncle Che, what are you doing?

06:08.600 --> 06:10.160
What are you doing? Uncle Che…

06:19.320 --> 06:20.720
Get away!

06:54.840 --> 06:57.120
Let go of me! Help!

06:57.200 --> 07:00.080
Uncle Che!
Aren't you afraid of going to jail?

07:01.880 --> 07:03.360
Ever since I married into this family,

07:04.800 --> 07:06.440
I've noticed

07:06.520 --> 07:08.840
something off about Che Xingde's gaze.

07:10.080 --> 07:11.360
I've heard from Wen Ming

07:12.760 --> 07:13.800
about what happened to you, too.

07:16.760 --> 07:18.520
When they bought that house,

07:18.600 --> 07:21.720
Che Xingde covered most of the cost.

07:23.600 --> 07:25.360
So, they all put up with it

07:26.080 --> 07:27.640
and told me to endure it, too.

07:28.160 --> 07:29.520
They just told me to be extra careful.

07:29.600 --> 07:31.600
Why is the door open?
Who left the door open?

07:32.120 --> 07:35.000
Say it again. Say it again!

07:36.640 --> 07:38.400
Let go! Let go of her!

07:38.480 --> 07:40.280
Did you hear me? Let go!

07:40.360 --> 07:42.160
- Say it!
- Let go!

07:42.240 --> 07:43.640
Let go!

07:44.280 --> 07:45.120
Mom!

07:45.200 --> 07:47.000
Mom! He's trying to kill me!

07:47.080 --> 07:48.400
- It's okay! Stay calm!
- Call the police!

07:48.480 --> 07:49.840
- Mom! Mom!
- Let Mom see…

07:49.920 --> 07:51.200
- Mom! Call the police!
- It's okay!

07:51.280 --> 07:54.560
I know. He always goes crazy
when he gets drunk.

07:54.640 --> 07:55.960
Went crazy, huh?

07:57.280 --> 07:58.120
- You went crazy?
- I'm leaving!

07:58.200 --> 07:59.760
Do it again!

07:59.840 --> 08:02.840
All right. I know it. I know it.

08:02.920 --> 08:03.760
It's okay.

08:04.280 --> 08:06.040
Let's talk outside. Let's talk outside.

08:06.560 --> 08:07.880
Still dare to act wild again?

08:07.960 --> 08:10.000
Still dare to get drunk again? Move.

08:12.160 --> 08:14.000
Calm down. It's okay.

08:14.520 --> 08:16.200
Here. Have a seat first.

08:16.880 --> 08:18.080
Sit down.

08:23.400 --> 08:25.760
It's okay. It's okay. Did you hear me?

08:26.840 --> 08:27.760
Listen to me.

08:28.480 --> 08:32.000
About this…
You absolutely must not call the police.

08:32.080 --> 08:35.120
If the police get involved,
everyone will know.

08:35.200 --> 08:36.919
A lie will become the truth.

08:37.000 --> 08:39.240
Then… Then how will you face other people?

08:39.320 --> 08:40.360
Right?

08:40.440 --> 08:41.559
I'm telling you,

08:41.640 --> 08:44.080
your Uncle Che
always gets like this when he is drunk,

08:44.159 --> 08:45.160
losing his mind.

08:45.800 --> 08:49.240
About this,
I will make things right for you.

08:49.320 --> 08:51.200
Trust me. I will protect you.

08:52.480 --> 08:54.360
I'll deal with your Uncle Che.

09:13.080 --> 09:14.560
Don't be mad, sister.

09:19.840 --> 09:20.960
Are you out of your mind?

09:22.400 --> 09:23.360
Who is she?

09:23.960 --> 09:26.080
She's Wen Ming's wife!

09:26.160 --> 09:27.960
She's my daughter-in-law!

09:28.040 --> 09:30.640
I didn't care about the others,
but now… now…

09:30.720 --> 09:32.640
you're going after my daughter-in-law?

09:32.720 --> 09:33.920
Have you lost it?

09:41.400 --> 09:42.720
I didn't do anything.

09:43.920 --> 09:45.040
"Didn't do anything"?

09:45.560 --> 09:47.240
If I hadn't walked in just now,

09:47.320 --> 09:49.360
you would've choked her to death!

09:50.080 --> 09:51.920
She came on to me first.

09:52.760 --> 09:54.320
Oh? She seduced you?

09:54.920 --> 09:57.960
You forget that girl next door,
Mr. Guo's daughter?

09:58.040 --> 10:00.000
You said the same thing about her.

10:00.080 --> 10:02.680
You know the truth better than anyone.

10:03.400 --> 10:06.120
What now? You want to kill another one?

10:06.200 --> 10:09.120
- Another one, huh?
- Sister, stop nagging.

10:09.200 --> 10:10.640
You're so annoying!

10:11.160 --> 10:13.120
Well, now you think I'm annoying?

10:13.720 --> 10:16.680
But when I helped you bury her body,
I wasn't annoying then?

10:16.760 --> 10:18.920
Do you even have a conscience?

10:21.440 --> 10:24.160
Sister, don't be mad.

10:25.720 --> 10:27.720
I was wrong.

10:28.720 --> 10:29.720
I swear…

10:30.760 --> 10:32.680
I won't do it again. Never again.

10:33.200 --> 10:34.200
All right?

10:35.880 --> 10:37.000
Listen to me.

10:38.120 --> 10:40.240
Just act like nothing happened today.

10:41.280 --> 10:42.880
Just say you were drunk. Understand?

10:42.960 --> 10:44.240
Wasn't I drunk anyway?

10:44.320 --> 10:45.400
- You…
- Look at you.

10:47.760 --> 10:50.440
When I found out Che Xingde
killed someone for this,

10:51.080 --> 10:52.640
I was so scared,
I almost dropped my phone.

10:53.760 --> 10:57.160
But deep down, I knew I had to stay calm.

10:57.960 --> 11:01.280
I had to call the police,
or else, the next one to die would be me.

11:04.120 --> 11:05.160
You're very brave.

11:09.160 --> 11:10.240
All right.

11:10.960 --> 11:12.960
I shouldn't shed tears for that villain.

11:16.440 --> 11:18.920
Talking to you makes me feel a lot better.

11:22.880 --> 11:24.680
I'm not afraid of getting hurt.

11:26.120 --> 11:28.840
I want the truth to come to light.

11:31.040 --> 11:32.000
It will.

11:33.840 --> 11:35.240
We're not just victims.

11:36.720 --> 11:38.400
We are people
who bravely protected ourselves.

11:42.120 --> 11:43.160
Yifan.

11:46.160 --> 11:47.880
Ms. Qian said we should head over now.

11:49.800 --> 11:51.040
I'll go get ready.

11:58.960 --> 12:00.120
Thank you for today.

12:02.240 --> 12:04.040
If anything comes up, reach out anytime.

12:20.560 --> 12:23.520
The victim's description
matches the missing person, Guo Ling.

12:23.600 --> 12:26.000
She was murdered while
studying at Beiyu High School.

12:26.880 --> 12:29.960
Guo Ling, do you remember me?

12:48.240 --> 12:51.880
I'll pay you back for the bus fare later.
We probably live nearby.

12:52.400 --> 12:53.880
It's fine. No need.

12:56.120 --> 12:57.320
Thank you, then.

12:58.880 --> 13:01.120
By the way, I'm Wen Yifan.

13:01.200 --> 13:02.040
What about you?

13:02.880 --> 13:03.920
I'm Guo Ling.

13:06.480 --> 13:09.760
I just transferred to Beiyu High School.
I'm in Class Four.

13:09.840 --> 13:11.920
- What about you?
- I'm in Class Eight.

13:12.680 --> 13:15.160
Class Eight? That's the advanced class.

13:15.240 --> 13:17.200
You must be really smart.

13:32.920 --> 13:34.960
Call me when you're done with work.

13:35.040 --> 13:35.880
SANG YAN

13:49.280 --> 13:50.280
Off work?

13:50.840 --> 13:52.240
Where are you? At the hotel?

13:53.800 --> 13:54.640
I found a guesthouse.

13:55.840 --> 13:57.400
- Are you tired?
- I'm okay.

13:58.760 --> 13:59.760
Sang Yan.

14:01.200 --> 14:03.160
Something happened with Che Xingde.

14:04.840 --> 14:08.120
He's a suspect in this murder case.

14:08.200 --> 14:09.240
He's still on the run.

14:11.520 --> 14:14.080
Maybe… Maybe I'm overthinking.

14:14.160 --> 14:15.600
But I'm worried he might come after you.

14:16.800 --> 14:19.080
Be extra careful when you go out, okay?

14:19.160 --> 14:22.920
This time, you went to Beiyu
just for this?

14:24.880 --> 14:27.560
Why are you always worrying
about me, a grown man?

14:27.640 --> 14:29.160
Wen Shuangjiang,

14:29.840 --> 14:31.560
you're the one who needs to be careful.

14:33.640 --> 14:36.520
And also,

14:38.480 --> 14:40.880
make sure to listen to that recording pen.

14:43.920 --> 14:46.800
With you here in person,
why should I bother with a recording?

14:46.880 --> 14:50.760
Saying some things out loud
just feels too cheesy.

14:54.600 --> 14:55.600
Oh, right.

14:55.680 --> 14:57.600
Today,

14:57.680 --> 15:00.040
I ran into a policewoman I used to know.

15:01.640 --> 15:03.800
Remember when I reported it back then?

15:03.880 --> 15:08.080
After I moved out of my Uncle Wen's house,
she took me in for a while.

15:09.000 --> 15:11.200
Seeing her today made me happy.

15:12.200 --> 15:13.320
It brought back a lot of feelings.

15:15.160 --> 15:17.800
She was really good to me.
Her daughter, Chen Xi, was too.

15:18.440 --> 15:21.640
Next time we get a chance,
let's visit her together.

15:21.720 --> 15:22.840
Sure.

15:26.520 --> 15:29.000
What about when Chen Xi gets married?
Let's go together.

15:29.560 --> 15:33.000
I saw on her social media
that her boyfriend proposed.

15:34.720 --> 15:37.120
I'm not sure when exactly
the wedding will be.

15:37.200 --> 15:39.120
We'll see if you're free
when the time comes.

15:42.400 --> 15:43.680
Wen Shuangjiang,

15:45.320 --> 15:46.480
are you hinting at something?

15:47.000 --> 15:48.240
What?

15:50.000 --> 15:51.920
Your birthday's coming up, isn't it?

15:52.440 --> 15:55.600
Make sure to wish
for something good this year.

15:56.640 --> 15:58.040
And I, as always,

15:59.160 --> 16:00.320
will make it happen.

16:01.440 --> 16:02.840
I'll hang up now.

16:02.920 --> 16:05.200
All right. If you're tired, get some rest.

16:05.920 --> 16:06.800
Goodnight.

16:40.960 --> 16:41.960
Coming.

16:51.920 --> 16:52.760
Hello, Mr. Guo.

16:53.960 --> 16:55.200
Who are you looking for?

16:56.320 --> 16:59.720
I'm a friend of Guo Ling.
I want to visit her.

17:02.480 --> 17:03.760
Please come in.

17:36.680 --> 17:38.760
I'm a reporter from Nanwu TV.

17:38.840 --> 17:41.560
But don't worry, I won't interview you.

17:43.920 --> 17:44.760
Have a seat.

17:59.880 --> 18:01.640
When Ling was three,

18:02.440 --> 18:03.840
her mother passed away.

18:05.840 --> 18:07.600
I was busy running my stall,

18:08.240 --> 18:09.760
up early and home late,
barely having time for her.

18:11.280 --> 18:14.520
She was always a well-behaved,
quiet child.

18:14.600 --> 18:17.480
She would often hide away in her room,
writing things on her own.

18:18.520 --> 18:20.000
But I never encouraged her.

18:20.640 --> 18:22.480
I always thought
the things she wrote about,

18:22.560 --> 18:24.120
romance, dreams…

18:24.640 --> 18:26.040
were just unrealistic.

18:26.960 --> 18:27.960
That night,

18:30.280 --> 18:31.240
we had an argument.

18:33.040 --> 18:34.960
It was the first time
she ever talked back to me.

18:36.280 --> 18:37.360
I never thought…

18:40.960 --> 18:42.640
it'd be the last.

18:44.000 --> 18:44.840
Ling.

18:45.680 --> 18:47.040
Why are you just sitting there?

18:47.120 --> 18:49.960
Come help me
sort things for tomorrow's stall.

18:52.520 --> 18:54.920
Dad, look at what I wrote!

18:55.000 --> 18:56.760
I really love writing.

18:57.280 --> 18:59.840
- I want to get published.
- I don't want to see it.

18:59.920 --> 19:02.680
Who's going to read
that worthless nonsense?

19:03.440 --> 19:04.960
Dad, don't say that.

19:05.680 --> 19:07.920
My dream is to become
a bestselling author!

19:08.000 --> 19:09.160
I have a dream, too!

19:10.240 --> 19:11.520
My dream

19:12.040 --> 19:15.360
is figuring out how to make money
so I can put food on the table.

19:15.880 --> 19:17.920
But I can't just spend

19:18.000 --> 19:20.520
my whole life
selling goods with you outside.

19:21.240 --> 19:22.560
I have my own dreams.

19:25.960 --> 19:27.360
What's wrong with selling things?

19:27.960 --> 19:29.560
Does it embarrass you?

19:30.280 --> 19:32.440
Writing novels can make money, too.

19:33.560 --> 19:36.640
You? Make money from writing? Let me see.

19:38.200 --> 19:40.640
Where's the money? Money? Where is it?

19:42.360 --> 19:43.400
If you're not helping, just go to bed!

19:44.000 --> 19:45.000
Unbelievable!

19:49.960 --> 19:51.640
I never thought…

19:52.600 --> 19:54.480
after she said those words,

19:55.160 --> 19:57.160
she'd never come back.

19:58.960 --> 20:00.160
All these years,

20:01.400 --> 20:03.560
I thought she was mad at me,

20:04.080 --> 20:07.120
hiding away, writing,
refusing to come home.

20:08.400 --> 20:09.680
Tell me…

20:10.200 --> 20:12.560
If back then,
I had cared just a little more,

20:12.640 --> 20:15.040
maybe she wouldn't have run away.

20:15.560 --> 20:16.800
Maybe by now,

20:18.960 --> 20:21.960
she really would've made
a name for herself

20:22.800 --> 20:25.480
and become the author
she always dreamed of being.

20:29.880 --> 20:32.960
I should've been the father she relied on.

20:33.480 --> 20:34.320
But…

20:36.080 --> 20:39.360
I was the one who led her to that monster.

20:41.440 --> 20:42.680
I deserve to die.

20:43.520 --> 20:45.360
- I deserve to die!
- Mr. Guo, stop!

20:45.880 --> 20:47.040
This isn't your fault.

20:47.760 --> 20:48.960
Calm down.

20:49.600 --> 20:51.240
She let her guard down

20:51.880 --> 20:54.560
because he was the neighbor.

20:57.640 --> 21:00.400
Don't worry. Once the verdict is out,
I'll report it as it is.

21:00.480 --> 21:02.840
I just hope no one else
goes through the same thing.

21:04.080 --> 21:05.080
Thank you.

21:06.640 --> 21:07.520
Thank you.

21:19.520 --> 21:21.000
- Hello?
- What's the situation?

21:21.680 --> 21:23.400
Che Xingde is still on the run.

21:23.480 --> 21:26.480
But Che Yanqin has been detained, I think.

21:26.560 --> 21:27.680
Are you coming back to Nanwu?

21:28.400 --> 21:30.200
- When will you be back?
- We're planning to head back soon.

21:30.280 --> 21:32.680
But I just got a call.

21:32.760 --> 21:35.120
They want me at the police station
to assist with the investigation.

21:35.840 --> 21:36.800
Also…

21:37.440 --> 21:39.840
Che Xingde might be back in Nanwu.

21:39.920 --> 21:42.440
Be extra careful when you go out, okay?

21:42.520 --> 21:43.680
You're the one who should be careful.

21:45.600 --> 21:46.760
I'll be waiting for you at home.

21:54.800 --> 21:58.560
TEA

22:20.520 --> 22:24.360
NANWU TV STATION

22:24.440 --> 22:26.360
- Did you see that?
- Yifan,

22:26.440 --> 22:27.760
I sent you the files. I'm heading out.

22:27.840 --> 22:29.120
- All right, take care.
- Bye.

22:29.200 --> 22:30.040
I'm leaving now, Yifan.

22:30.120 --> 22:33.680
Just swap those two around.

22:33.760 --> 22:35.360
See? Super simple. Got it?

22:36.520 --> 22:38.080
- All right, finish up and head home.
- Thanks.

22:38.160 --> 22:39.000
Bye.

22:43.960 --> 22:48.040
Yifan, why hasn't
that relative of yours been reported?

22:51.080 --> 22:54.120
The police are still investigating.
We're waiting for the confirmed results.

22:55.480 --> 22:57.280
Hope they can bring that villain
to justice soon.

22:58.160 --> 22:59.240
I hope so, too.

22:59.760 --> 23:01.680
All right, I'll get going.

23:01.760 --> 23:02.720
You should head home soon, too.

23:02.800 --> 23:03.840
Stay safe.

23:09.960 --> 23:10.800
SANG YAN

23:10.880 --> 23:14.000
Let me know when you're done working.
I'll come pick you up.

23:15.480 --> 23:17.000
WEN YIFAN

23:17.080 --> 23:19.160
Okay. Come at 8:30.

24:08.480 --> 24:10.200
If I ever hit rock bottom,

24:11.640 --> 24:13.920
no matter where you go,
I'll always find you.

24:33.160 --> 24:34.560
I'm not feeling great today.

24:35.240 --> 24:36.840
I think I'll just head home.

24:39.960 --> 24:42.560
Lower the overall saturation a bit more.

24:42.640 --> 24:43.480
And then, these two characters

24:43.560 --> 24:44.480
- Sang Yan.
- should be enlarged.

24:45.160 --> 24:46.720
- Going or not?
- These two?

24:46.800 --> 24:48.600
- To Overtime.
- I'm not going.

24:51.320 --> 24:53.880
- Right. Right here.
- Okay.

24:55.200 --> 24:56.280
Does this part need any adjustments?

24:57.960 --> 25:00.040
Bro. Why aren't you going again?

25:02.800 --> 25:04.440
I've got to pick up
my girlfriend from work.

25:07.000 --> 25:09.560
You two can't stand
even a little time apart, huh?

25:09.640 --> 25:10.480
Right?

25:11.680 --> 25:12.640
When are you free?

25:12.720 --> 25:14.920
Let's get together for a hot pot.
It has been ages since we hung out.

25:15.600 --> 25:16.760
With whom?

25:17.640 --> 25:19.240
A bunch of couples.

25:20.680 --> 25:22.320
Sure. Wait for me.

25:26.880 --> 25:27.720
Hey.

25:33.560 --> 25:36.320
I'm wrapping up here. Come pick me up now.

25:37.680 --> 25:39.600
OKAY

26:02.720 --> 26:05.920
NANWU TV STATION

26:33.800 --> 26:34.960
Che Xingde is still on the run.

26:35.560 --> 26:37.960
But Che Yanqin has been detained, I think.

26:39.160 --> 26:42.760
Also… Che Xingde might be back in Nanwu.

26:56.680 --> 26:58.000
Hello. I'd like to report a crime.

26:59.120 --> 27:02.840
I'm at the entrance of Nanwu TV station.
I spotted the suspect, Che Xingde.

27:03.360 --> 27:04.240
Yes.

27:21.320 --> 27:23.240
He's been harassing me nonstop.

27:36.720 --> 27:38.240
Luckily, they came home early.

27:51.440 --> 27:52.320
What are you doing here?

27:52.400 --> 27:54.080
None of your business! Let go of me.

27:54.160 --> 27:55.360
Let go!

28:11.880 --> 28:13.200
Tired from running all this time?

28:14.640 --> 28:16.080
Wouldn't it be easier to sit back
and enjoy your time in prison?

28:19.200 --> 28:20.280
Why don't you try it yourself?

29:15.480 --> 29:16.920
Why weren't you answering your phone?

29:27.320 --> 29:28.720
- Hello?
- Hello?

29:28.800 --> 29:29.720
Who's this?

29:29.800 --> 29:30.880
I just found this phone.

29:30.960 --> 29:32.720
The owner got stabbed in a fight.

29:32.800 --> 29:34.440
What? Where are you guys?

30:09.080 --> 30:10.480
Here!

30:11.080 --> 30:12.160
I'm here!

30:12.920 --> 30:13.760
Here!

30:13.840 --> 30:15.680
- Were you the one who answered the phone?
- Yeah.

30:15.760 --> 30:18.720
- Where is he now?
- He just got taken to the hospital.

30:18.800 --> 30:19.720
Are you his girlfriend?

30:21.440 --> 30:22.920
Is his name Sang Yan?

30:23.000 --> 30:23.960
I don't know.

30:24.040 --> 30:25.720
I just saw a tall, skinny guy.

30:26.520 --> 30:28.400
His hands were covered in blood.

30:28.480 --> 30:31.320
His stomach got slashed, too.
The blood just kept flowing.

30:31.400 --> 30:33.000
That much blood…

30:33.080 --> 30:33.920
Did the medics say anything?

30:34.000 --> 30:36.160
He was taken to Nanwu Central Hospital.

30:36.240 --> 30:37.880
- Thank you.
- His phone!

30:41.480 --> 30:42.960
- Thanks.
- Hurry!

31:23.800 --> 31:25.880
It'll be okay… It'll be okay…

31:28.360 --> 31:29.320
I love you.

31:30.840 --> 31:32.160
So, so much.

31:35.720 --> 31:36.760
Do you understand?

31:48.560 --> 31:50.440
Can you go any faster?

31:50.960 --> 31:52.480
See? So much traffic.

32:00.320 --> 32:01.520
Miss, are you all right?

32:18.640 --> 32:20.520
Wen Shuangjiang.

32:21.240 --> 32:22.520
Stay safe at work.

32:23.040 --> 32:26.880
Your man wants you home safe.

32:29.680 --> 32:31.480
Wen Shuangjiang.

32:32.320 --> 32:34.000
Stay safe at work.

32:34.080 --> 32:37.760
Your man wants you home safe.

32:43.840 --> 32:46.640
Sir, is there another route we can take?

32:46.720 --> 32:49.280
Nope. What's going on today?

32:49.360 --> 32:50.400
Traffic's a total mess.

32:51.880 --> 32:53.200
Just pull over here, please.

32:58.800 --> 33:00.640
UNKNOWN CALLER

33:01.520 --> 33:02.480
Hello?

33:05.640 --> 33:07.000
Is that you, Sang Yan?

33:07.760 --> 33:08.840
Wen Shuangjiang…

33:08.920 --> 33:10.640
Are you okay? Where are you hurt?

33:10.720 --> 33:13.400
I'm fine. Just a small cut on my hand.

33:13.480 --> 33:15.960
You call that fine? I saw so much blood.

33:16.040 --> 33:18.200
Most of it was probably Che Xingde's.

33:18.720 --> 33:19.560
I swear. I'm okay.

33:19.640 --> 33:22.240
Don't worry so much.
I already told you. I'm fine.

33:23.200 --> 33:26.520
I'll head home later.
I still need to make a statement here.

33:26.600 --> 33:27.520
It might take some time.

33:27.600 --> 33:29.320
Where are you now? I'll come to you.

33:29.400 --> 33:31.480
I'm at… Central Hospital's emergency room.

33:32.000 --> 33:32.960
Got it.

33:36.440 --> 33:37.640
Sir. Thank you.

33:38.440 --> 33:39.280
Okay, Mr. Sang.

33:39.360 --> 33:41.880
Once you're done with treatment,
we'll come back to check in with you.

33:41.960 --> 33:43.000
All right. Thank you.

33:53.400 --> 33:54.800
TRIAGE COUNTER

34:00.840 --> 34:01.760
Excuse me.

34:01.840 --> 34:04.800
Is there a patient named Sang Yan here?

34:04.880 --> 34:06.040
Over there.

34:06.120 --> 34:07.320
- Thank you.
- No problem.

34:22.639 --> 34:25.480
Besides the eight stitches on your hand,
is your stomach wound all right?

34:26.480 --> 34:27.600
- It's fine now.
- Okay then.

34:27.679 --> 34:30.440
If there's any update, let us know.

34:31.360 --> 34:32.920
Got it. Thanks.

34:44.560 --> 34:45.639
Just a small cut?

34:51.199 --> 34:52.239
A small cut needed eight stitches?

34:54.280 --> 34:57.400
Well… not only do you not care about me,
but you're actually mad at me?

34:58.640 --> 34:59.680
Why did you go after him?

35:00.320 --> 35:01.720
What? Did I do something wrong?

35:02.320 --> 35:04.240
When you saw him,
why didn't you just call the police?

35:05.880 --> 35:08.280
- What if he ran away?
- Do you always have to play the hero?

35:19.440 --> 35:20.320
What's wrong with you?

35:23.120 --> 35:24.280
I don't like you doing this.

35:24.360 --> 35:26.040
Can you just stay out of this?

35:26.120 --> 35:27.600
Don't make me regret
telling you this, okay?

35:27.680 --> 35:30.880
Go to work. Come home.
Just be safe. Is that so hard?

35:30.960 --> 35:32.760
I don't even care about this anymore.

35:32.840 --> 35:35.760
Even if I want Che Xingde
to rot in prison forever,

35:36.360 --> 35:39.800
that thought…
doesn't compare to my fear of losing you!

35:56.520 --> 35:57.760
Why aren't you happy?

36:00.680 --> 36:01.960
Che Xingde was caught.

36:02.960 --> 36:04.800
Your aunt paid the price.

36:06.440 --> 36:08.240
That girl finally got justice.

36:10.880 --> 36:11.840
And…

36:15.200 --> 36:17.920
this time, I protected you.

36:22.880 --> 36:24.800
I actually care a lot. I care so much.

36:24.880 --> 36:25.760
Back then, when I said
I wouldn't chase after you,

36:25.840 --> 36:26.800
I really meant it.

36:28.320 --> 36:29.280
But now I think…

36:31.320 --> 36:33.480
why does a man like me
care so much about pride?

36:37.240 --> 36:38.720
Why did I

36:40.240 --> 36:42.440
hold this grudge for so many years?

36:51.640 --> 36:53.400
Back then, young and reckless,

36:55.000 --> 36:58.480
loving someone meant giving you everything

37:00.520 --> 37:01.800
and lowering my pride over and over.

37:03.000 --> 37:06.320
But… Vut at the same time,

37:08.040 --> 37:09.840
your words could tear me apart so easily.

37:09.920 --> 37:11.520
I told myself,

37:13.520 --> 37:15.760
for the rest of my life,
I would never step into your world again.

37:18.400 --> 37:19.800
But I knew I was lying.

37:21.400 --> 37:22.720
I knew all I could do
was wait, hopelessly.

37:23.320 --> 37:26.360
Still, for the sake of dignity,
for the sake of saving face,

37:28.200 --> 37:29.360
I thought…

37:34.560 --> 37:36.680
I could never be the one
to reach out first again.

37:36.760 --> 37:37.640
But now, I regret it.

37:37.720 --> 37:41.640
I regret spending two whole years
only thinking about

37:42.560 --> 37:44.520
how I was the weaker one
in this relationship.

37:48.960 --> 37:51.240
Yet, not once
did I try to pull you out of it.

37:56.360 --> 38:00.200
I never even noticed the pain and despair
you kept buried so deep.

38:02.520 --> 38:04.360
Stop. This was my fault.

38:04.440 --> 38:05.720
It's not on you.

38:05.800 --> 38:08.080
The only one to blame
is that villain, Che Xingde.

38:09.840 --> 38:12.600
So, Wen Shuangjiang, I did it this time.

38:13.320 --> 38:14.880
Can you be happy for me?

38:14.960 --> 38:17.120
I put that villain behind bars.

38:34.720 --> 38:36.320
Can you stop crying now?

38:40.520 --> 38:42.800
Come on. I'm the one
in pain from the stitches.

38:43.480 --> 38:44.960
Why are you crying so much?

38:48.440 --> 38:49.440
What are you doing?

38:52.320 --> 38:54.120
If you keep crying, I'll…

38:55.240 --> 38:56.440
Take care.

38:58.520 --> 38:59.880
Don't you feel bad for me?

39:01.920 --> 39:03.240
All right. I'm fine now.

39:04.520 --> 39:05.880
It doesn't hurt at all.

39:07.280 --> 39:09.160
Wen Shuangjiang, what's with you?

39:12.000 --> 39:14.600
Weren't you covering this news?

39:14.680 --> 39:16.040
How could I be in the mood for that?

39:16.120 --> 39:19.960
When my house burned down,
you were eager to report on it.

39:20.040 --> 39:21.400
That was different.

39:22.720 --> 39:23.880
All right. It's over now. Let's go.

39:23.960 --> 39:25.240
Take care.

39:25.760 --> 39:28.040
I'm really fine. Just a few scratches.

39:28.560 --> 39:30.960
- Are you okay?
- Take this jacket for me.

39:32.520 --> 39:35.200
Even injured, you're still so talkative.

39:36.040 --> 39:37.920
- Are you okay?
- Okay.

39:38.960 --> 39:41.800
What else can I do? Stay here on vacation?

40:03.600 --> 40:07.880
THE STORY IS NOT OVER YET…

40:17.240 --> 40:19.080
If something had
really happened back then,

40:19.600 --> 40:21.400
you'd already feel this knife.

40:24.600 --> 40:27.120
I've finally caught
the shadow that haunted you.

40:30.000 --> 40:31.160
This is good.

40:34.280 --> 40:35.800
From now on…

40:39.240 --> 40:40.760
your world will only have light.

40:54.600 --> 40:56.560
No matter where you run in this life,

40:57.680 --> 40:58.920
I will chase you to the ends of the earth.

43:57.120 --> 43:57.960
HUGE THANKS TO EVERYONE INVOLVED
AND TO ALL THE FANS OF THE FIRST FROST!

43:58.040 --> 43:58.880
TREAT YOURSELF WELL
AND THE WORLD WILL HOLD MORE LOVE FOR YOU!
